
<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Mass Script Creator (MSC)</h1>
  <p>Bulk creation of 1 page scripts for ApP, TxP & MWP</p>
</div>
<div>
Create comma delimited lines of ScriptName, ActionName and URL e.g.
<pre>
Apple,Appe Store HomePage,http://www.apple.com/uk/thestore
BBC,BBC News,http://news.bbc.co.uk/
MS,Microsoft HomePage,http://www.microsoft.com
etc.
</pre>
</div>
<form enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/msc/generate" method="post" class="form-horizontal">
        <div class="control-group">
            <label class="control-label" for="scriptType">Script Type</label>
            <div class="controls">
                <select id="scriptType" name="scriptType" required>
                    <option value="bpdo">ApP BPDO</option>
                    <option value="app">ApP Default</option>
                    <option value="txpdlc">TxP Download Cycle 1 + Timer 3 seconds</option>
                    <option value="txpinactivity">TxP HTTP Inactivity 1000 msec</option>
                    <option value="mwp">MWP Default</option>

                </select>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="control-group">
            <label class="control-label" for="urls">CSV</label>
            <div class="controls">
                <textarea class="input-xxlarge" rows="5" id="urls" name="urls" placeholder="ScriptName,ActionName,Url" required></textarea>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="control-group">
            <div class="controls">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Generate Scripts</button>
            </div>
        </div>
</form>
